snippet: The British Mail steamship Asia, Capt. JUDKINS, arrived at this port yesterday morning, from Liverpool, whence she sailed on the 27th September. On the 9th inst., at 6 A.M., the Asia passed the steamship Africa, hence for Liverpool....
lead_paragraph: The British Mail steamship Asia, Capt. JUDKINS, arrived at this port yesterday morning, from Liverpool, whence she sailed on the 27th September. On the 9th inst., at 6 A.M., the Asia passed the steamship Africa, hence for Liverpool.
